The Blender Cloud is a web infrastructure serving tutorial videos and files to thousands of users.

The service was launched together with a worldwide crowdfunding campaign to support Blender's 5th open movie *['Cosmos Laundromat'](https://gooseberry.blender.org)*, codenamed 'Gooseberry project'.  
The framework uses Python, Flask and JavaScript.
